[107250176562458707418,100743520699027626603,The owner is very friendly and extremely helpful. They have lots of rare wines at surprisingly reasonable prices, and the atmosphere is great. It's clean and comfortable with a bar to taste at, and there's plenty of room to relax and share a drink with a friend. They even had a few soft comfortable chairs off to the side of the bar. If you love wine, you have to check this place out.]
